Monitor
Necromancers can quickly access information concerning their current
well-being through the use of the 'hp' command. In addition to standard
information about HP and SP, a Necromancer will see two meters labeled
"BLIGHT" and "DEATH". These two meters correspond to the two ~>runes<~
that augment their spells. A Necromancer will also notice a health bar
for each of their ~>followers<~, and information about current effects
that are active.
